CompanyDescription.label: Company Description
CompanyDescription.value: RenaissanceRe Holdings Ltd provides reinsurance and insurance solutions and related services. The company's core products include property catastrophe and specialty reinsurance risks. Revenue is primarily derived from three sources: net premiums earned from the insurance and insurance products sold; net investment income from the investment of capital funds and cash; and other income from the company's joint ventures, advisory services, and other items. The reportable segments of the company are property and casualty & specialty.
